Quickstrike:





"Well, this is it," Quickstrike said to Dark Mouse and leaned over to 
press the button on the side of the door frame. The door slid opened, 
revealing a dark room. He helped her in, and reached at least two 
long fingers to a switch that lighten the room. It reached enough for 
a dim glow.
